---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Refund & Cancellation Policy — Thee Rainers"
  description="Thee Rainers refund and cancellation policy for digital products, subscriptions, workshops, and coaching."
>
  <section class="bg-[#F7F5F2] px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-20 pt-32 pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">

      <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="font-black text-[#141414] text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-tight tracking-tight mb-3">Refund &amp; Cancellation Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-[#141414]/40 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: 26 May 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-legal">

        <p>
          Questions about a purchase? Email <a href="mailto:rainers@stepintoring.com">rainers@stepintoring.com</a> — we will always do our best to help.
        </p>

        <h2>1. Digital products and downloads (Blueprints)</h2>
        <p>
          The Footwork Blueprint, Shadowboxing Blueprint, and Bundle are digital downloads delivered immediately or within minutes of purchase via a secure link sent to your email address. Because the content is delivered digitally and is accessible immediately after purchase, <strong>all digital product sales are final and non-refundable once the download link has been accessed or the file has been downloaded.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          If you have not accessed your download link and wish to request a refund, contact us within 48 hours of purchase at <a href="mailto:rainers@stepintoring.com">rainers@stepintoring.com</a> with your order details and we will consider your request.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you did not receive your download link, email us and we will resend it immediately.
        </p>

        <h2>2. Monthly subscriptions (Blueprints + Q&A access)</h2>
        <p>
          You can cancel your subscription at any time from your account or by emailing <a href="mailto:rainers@stepintoring.com">rainers@stepintoring.com</a>. Cancellation stops all future renewals. You keep full access until the end of your current paid period. We do not refund the portion of a billing period already started, unless required by law.
        </p>

        <h2>3. Live workshops (Defense Workshop)</h2>
        <p>
          Workshop tickets are non-refundable. If you are unable to attend the live session, you will receive the full workshop recording at no additional charge. If the session is cancelled by us, you will receive a full refund or a credit towards a future session at your choice.
        </p>

        <h2>4. Workshop Replay (on-demand)</h2>
        <p>
          The Workshop Replay is a digital product granting 7-day access to an on-demand video. Because access is granted immediately upon purchase, <strong>the Workshop Replay is non-refundable once the access link has been used.</strong> If you have not accessed your link, contact us within 48 hours for a refund consideration.
        </p>

        <h2>5. Private Architecture (1-of-1 coaching)</h2>
        <p>
          Private Architecture engagements are non-refundable once the first session has taken place. We stand behind our work: if at any point you feel the coaching is not producing clear, measurable progress, we will continue sessions at no charge until it does.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Rescheduling:</strong> You may reschedule a session with at least 24 hours' notice. Sessions cancelled with less than 24 hours' notice, or where you do not attend without notice (no-show), are forfeited.
        </p>

        <h2>6. EU / EEA 14-day right of withdrawal</h2>
        <p>
          If you are a consumer in the European Union or European Economic Area, you have a statutory right to withdraw from a purchase within 14 days without giving a reason (the "cooling-off period"), subject to the following exceptions:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>If you <strong>explicitly consented to immediate performance</strong> of a service (for example, by requesting immediate access to a live session), the right of withdrawal is lost once performance begins.</li>
          <li>If you <strong>explicitly consented to immediate delivery</strong> of digital content (for example, by requesting that a download link be sent before the 14-day period expires), the right of withdrawal is lost once the content has been delivered and you have acknowledged this.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Where the right of withdrawal applies and has not been waived, contact us at <a href="mailto:rainers@stepintoring.com">rainers@stepintoring.com</a> within 14 days of your purchase to exercise this right. We will process your refund within 14 days of receiving your withdrawal notice.
        </p>

        <h2>7. How to request a refund or cancellation</h2>
        <p>
          Email <a href="mailto:rainers@stepintoring.com">rainers@stepintoring.com</a> with your name, email address used at checkout, the product purchased, and the reason for your request. We aim to respond within 2 business days.
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-legal {
    color: #141414;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .prose-legal h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: #141414;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .prose-legal p, .prose-legal li {
    color: #141414;
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }
  .prose-legal ul {
    padding-left: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .prose-legal li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .prose-legal a {
    color: #c84d3a;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .prose-legal a:hover {
    opacity: 0.75;
  }
  .prose-legal strong {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #141414;
  }
</style>
